|1/32 A || align=right|[[SK Sigma Olomouc|Olomouc]] || {{gris|2-2}} || align=left|OM
|- bgcolor=#EFEFEF
|1/32 R || align=right|OM || {{vert|4-0}} || align=left|Olomouc 
