|1/8 A || align=right|[[Association sportive de Monaco football club|Monaco]] || {{gris|2-2}} || align=left|OM
|- bgcolor=#EFEFEF
|1/8 R || align=right|OM || {{vert|1-0}} || align=left|Monaco 
