| {{1re}}-{{19e}} || - || Bordeaux (+1)
|- 
| {{19e}}-{{38e}} || PSG 0-1 Bordeaux || Bordeaux (+3)
|-
| {{38e}}-{{57e}} || Nantes 0-1 OM || Bordeaux (+1)
|- 
| {{57e}}-{{60e}} || PSG 1-1 Bordeaux || OM (+1)
